OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will
OL,6,Fremain mostly cloudy this evening and
OL,7,Ftonight with a few showers, and just
OL,8,Fone or two clear intervals, these
OL,9,Fmostly towards the morning.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FA mostly cloudy day. Mainly
OL,12,Fdry morning with just a few light
OL,13,Fshowers, then some more persistent
OL,14,Frain followed by heavy showers later.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,17,FRather cloudy with some showers on
OL,18,FThursday and early Friday. Brighter
OL,19,Fthereafter with sunny intervals and
OL,20,Fmore scattered showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
